Join the Movement
Every trade, every moustache, every $BRO holder helps make a difference. When you buy or sell $BRO, part of every transaction supports Movember — the world’s leading charity for men’s mental health and suicide prevention.

How You Help
Through Pump.fun’s creator fees, we’re donating 50% of all revenue directly to Movember.com to fund programs that help men open up, seek help early, and stay connected. The rest powers awareness, boosts visibility, and builds a movement that keeps the conversation alive.

A Mission Beyond the Memes
This isn’t just another token — it’s a symbol of solidarity. The goal is to turn memes into meaning and give crypto culture a cause worth holding for. Every trade fuels both fun and change.

Grow the Mo, Grow the Impact
The more $BRO spreads, the more support we can give. Together, we can become one of the largest Movember donors this year — showing that web3 can unite to raise funds, break stigma, and save lives.
